org.apache.flink.streaming.api.operators.async.queue

接口 AsyncResult

  • 所有已知子接口:
    AsyncCollectionResult<T>, AsyncWatermarkResult
    所有已知实现类:
    StreamElementQueueEntry, StreamRecordQueueEntry, WatermarkQueueEntry

    @Internal
public interface AsyncResult
    Asynchronous result returned by the StreamElementQueue. The asynchronous result can either be a Watermark or a collection of new output elements produced by the AsyncFunction.

    • 方法概要

      boolean isResultCollection()
      True fi the async result is a collection of output elements; otherwise false.
      boolean isWatermark()
      True if the async result is a Watermark; otherwise false.
